## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-102">カスタムの音声合成エンジンで音声プラットフォーム シンセサイザー インフラストラクチャに送信されたイベントの種類を定義する、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-102">Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-103">仕様は、設定によって実行、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A>プロパティの<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>に渡されるインスタンス、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A>実装するクラスのメンバー、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>に渡されたインターフェイス、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A>カスタム音声認識エンジンの上のメソッド実装<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-103">Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-104">音声プラットフォームのインフラストラクチャを通じてが処理されているイベントの種類を示す、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>プロパティを<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>speak 実装に渡されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-104">The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-105">値<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>このビットマスクを指定するには、場所のメンバー<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>イベントの種類に対応するビットの位置を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-105">The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="599e8-106">たとえば、WordBoundary が 5 (5) によって返される値の 5 番目のビットの意味の値を持つ<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>サイトが、イベントの種類をサポートしているかを示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-106">For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-107">次の例から継承するカスタムの音声合成の実装の一部は、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>の使用を使用して、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>と <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-107">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="599e8-108">実装 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-108">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="599e8-109">配列を受け取る<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>インスタンスし、の新しい配列を作成します。<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>に渡されるインスタンス、`Speak`メソッドを基になるの合成エンジン。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-109">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="599e8-110">場合、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>から列挙値がによって検出された、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A>プロパティを<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A>によって返される、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>の各プロパティ<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A>インスタンスが<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>、実装</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-110">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> enumeration value by found from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property of each <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> instance is <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, the implementation</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="599e8-111">読み上げるテキストで Americanism Britishisms に変換します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-111">Translates Americanism to Britishisms in the text to be spoken.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="599e8-112">場合、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>プロパティを<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>WordBoundary イベントの種類をサポートするインターフェイスの実装を提供する<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>シンセサイザーの進行状況バーが作成されたドライブにイベントを作成するインスタンスを使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-112">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> interfaces provided to the implementation support the WordBoundary event type, a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instance is used to create an event to drive a synthesizer progress meter is created.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="599e8-113">音声のレンダリング エンジンが呼び出され、変更されたと<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>配列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="599e8-113">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
private const int WordBoundaryFlag = 1 << (int)TtsEventId.WordBoundary;  
private readonly char[] spaces = new char[] { ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n' };  
internal struct UsVsUk  
{  
  internal string UK;  
  internal string US;  
}  
  
override public void Speak (TextFragment [] frags, IntPtr wfx, ITtsEngineSite site)  
{  
  TextFragment [] newFrags=new TextFragment[frags.Length];  
  
  for (int i=0;i<frags.Length;i++){  
    newFrags[i].State=frags[i].State;  
    //truncate  
    newFrags[i].TextToSpeak = frags[i].TextToSpeak.Substring(frags[i].TextOffset,  
                               frags[i].TextLength);  
    newFrags[i].TextLength = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Length;  
    newFrags[i].TextOffset = 0;  
    if (newFrags[i].State.Action == TtsEngineAction.Speak) {  
      //Us to UK conversion  
      foreach (UsVsUk term in TransList) {  
      newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Replace(term.US, term.UK);  
      }  
      //Generate progress meter events if supported  
      if ((site.EventInterest & WordBoundaryFlag) != 0) {  
      string[] subs = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Split(spaces);  
  
      foreach (string s in subs) {  
        int offset = newFrags[i].TextOffset;  
        SpeechEventInfo spEvent = new SpeechEventInfo((Int16)TtsEventId.WordBoundary,   
                (Int16)EventParameterType.Undefined,   
                 s.Length, new IntPtr(offset));  
        offset += s.Length;  
        if (s.Trim().Length > 0) {  
          SpeechEventInfo[] events = new SpeechEventInfo[1];  
          events[0] = spEvent;  
          site.AddEvents(events, 1);  
        }  
      }  
      }  
    }  
  }  
  
  _baseSynthesize.Speak(newFrags, wfx, site);  
  
}  
```
